  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is part of a larger study for which participants have already completed memory and
      thinking tests. In this study, investigators are trying to learn how deep-brain stimulation
      affects memory skills in essential tremor (ET) patients. We are especially trying to figure
      out how stimulation on each side of the brain may affect working memory.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
